            <!-- BEGIN: customer-engagement-fabric-TopBanner -->
            <div class="common-banner col-top-banner" data-config="{'backgroundColor':'#e3f4ff', 'backgroundImage':'//wacnppe.blob.core.chinacloudapi.cn/marketing-resource/media/images/production/customer-engagement-fabric_banner.png','imageHeight':'auto'}">
                <div class="common-banner-image">
                    <div class="common-banner-title">
                        <img src="//wacnppe.blob.core.chinacloudapi.cn/marketing-resource/media/images/production/customer-engagement-fabric_icon.svg" />
                        <h2>Customer Engagement Fabric <span style="color: #4d4d4d;font-family: '微软雅黑',regular;font-size: 20px;top: -6px;position: relative;display: inline;">(Preview)</span><span>Customer Engagement Fabric</span></h2>
                        <h4>Provides unified API to help App developers quickly build general functions such as notification, verification and payment. Through the improvement of development efficiency and unified management of user data, operational efficiency is improved.</h4>
                        <em><a href="/pricing/1rmb-trial/" id="customer-engagement-fabric_1rmb-trial">Apply for 1RMB Trial<i class="icon icon-arrow-right-thin"></i></a></em> <a href="/pricing/pia/" id="customer-engagement-fabric_pia">Buy Now<i class="icon icon-arrow-right-thin"></i></a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- END: customer-engagement-fabric-TopBanner --> <!-- BEGIN: customer-engagement-fabric-Content -->
            <div class="pricing-page-section">
                <p>Customer Engagement Fabric (CEF) brings together many local service providers to provide a series of basic services that allow interactive connectivity between the app and users, including multi-channel notification service, sign-in verification and aggregate functions for payment. These services can help the app to quickly implement relevant user connectivity functions, improve user engagement and analyze user behavior data to improve app operational efficiency.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="pricing-page-section">
                <h2>Notification service</h2>
                <p>Provides stable and efficient text message notification, email notification, App push with high arrive rate and intelligent Azure Notification Hubs (integration notification).</p>
            </div>
            <div class="pricing-page-section">
                <h2>Sign-in verification</h2>
                <p>Provides concise API to implement third-party sign-in and dynamic password verification so as to reduce development time and quickly get users.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="pricing-page-section">
                <h2>Aggregate functions for payment</h2>
                <p>Provides unified API to quickly implement third-party payment functions, unified management of user data and analysis of user behavior data.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="pricing-page-section">
				<h2>List of subservices (announced)</h2>
				<div class="message-box col-md-6">
					<h3>Text message service</h3>
					<ul>
						<li>Supports notification reminder, text message with verification code and marketing text messaging</li>
						<li>arrived in 5 seconds, 99% arrive rate</li>
						<li>Trip-Play, 10690 dedicated channels</li>
						<li>Fast API access, real-time data count</li>
					</ul>
					<p><a href="/home/features/customer-engagement-fabric/sms/">Find out more</a></p>
				</div>
                <div class="third-part col-md-6">
					<h3>Third-party sign-in service</h3>
					<ul>
						<li>Unified SDK, quickly build third-party sign-in</li>
						<li>Save time for developers</li>
						<li>Quickly get users</li>
						<li>Aggregates user information data for convenience in performing statistical analysis</li>
					</ul>
					<p><a href="/home/features/customer-engagement-fabric/social-login/">Find out more</a></p>
				</div>
